                     <persName id="t18741214-name-126" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18741214-name-126" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18741214-name-126" type="surname" value="ROBINSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18741214-name-126" type="given" value="ERNEST"></interp>ERNEST ROBINSON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-called</hi>). Amongst the proceedings which are pro<lb></lb>duced is the examination of the bankrupt before the County Court Judge and the examination of Chamberlain.</p>
